      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i really dont want to go to the er or anything if i dont have to. its just so expensive and the wait is always crazy. do u think it's really that bad? like honestly, if i just keep it iced and wrapped up for like 48 hours, would it be okay to just wait and see if the swelling goes down before i bother with a doctor?",
